The paper discusses the design of MIMO transmission systems with discrete input signals, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the design of transmission schemes for massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY) and multimedia systems (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the security aspects of MIMO transmission, which is a topic related to cryptography (cs.CR).
